{"type":"answer","id":210199,"parentType":"question","parentId":21315,"uid":9063,"contents":"那个日子谁也不知道，只有父知道：<br>\n<br>\n马太福音24:36<br>\n“至于那个日子、那个时刻，谁也不知道<a href=\"https://wol.jw.org/cmn-Hans/wol/bc/r23/lp-chs/1001061144/805\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\">+</a>，天上的天使不知道，儿子也不知道，只有我的父亲知道<a href=\"https://wol.jw.org/cmn-Hans/wol/bc/r23/lp-chs/1001061144/806\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\">+</a>。<br>\n<br>\n<br>\n要做的就是恒常守望，时刻做好准备：<br>\n<br>\n马太福音24:42<br>\n所以，你们要不断守望，因为你们不知道你们的主在什么日子来到<a href=\"https://wol.jw.org/cmn-Hans/wol/bc/r23/lp-chs/1001061144/812\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\">+</a><br>\n<br>\n<br>\n就像賊来一样，不会让你们猜得到。所以不要去猜：<br>\n<br>\n马太福音24:43-44<br>\n“有一件事你们要知道，一家的主人如果早知道几更天<a href=\"https://wol.jw.org/cmn-Hans/wol/fn/r23/lp-chs/1001061144/233\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\">*</a>有贼来<a href=\"https://wol.jw.org/cmn-Hans/wol/bc/r23/lp-chs/1001061144/813\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\">+</a>，就会保持警醒，不让贼挖洞进家里来<a href=\"https://wol.jw.org/cmn-Hans/wol/bc/r23/lp-chs/1001061144/814\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\">+</a>。<a href=\"https://wol.jw.org/cmn-Hans/wol/dx/r23/lp-chs/1001061144/24117\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\">44&nbsp;</a>所以你们也要做好准备<a href=\"https://wol.jw.org/cmn-Hans/wol/bc/r23/lp-chs/1001061144/815\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\">+</a>，因为人子会在你们认为不大可能的时刻来到。","date":"2020-03-19","agreeCount":9,"discussionCount":0}